reviews.text: Good for quick lunch
The environment is good, the store is big enough. And food is still qualified. But it is hard to find the location.
Good for 1 ppl go

Tried their deluxe bowl (I think that's what its called?) With level 4 spiciness. The noodles and soup base were very delicious. Also ordered a side of cucumber marinated in vinegar, which was also very tasty. Recommend trying this restaurant if you're into noodle soup.
Tomato soup is okay.

result.adr_address: 香港沙田橫壆街29C-E號
result.name: 譚仔雲南米線

reviews.text: 保持水準👌
有清湯底蕃茄湯底還有一抽嘅豬潤 環境舒服乾淨 值得一試
我個人覺得味道太濃不適合本人，可能其他人可以接受。

令人上癮，一試難忘。譚仔姐姐們親切。
店外在繁忙時間需要等待位子，多人輪侯。

自從譚仔出現之後，店舖的辣度參考圖，仔細地劃分特辣、大辣、中辣、小辣、2小辣 至 5小辣，最後10小辣，將辣分為9級。原本你覺得辣，我覺得無料到，現在一旦問「你食開咩辣㗎？」對方回應「三小辣」，彼此即心裡有數。餐牌上，最辣為特辣，但特辣是點一回事？仍然是個謎。其實有一種辣，是可以chok出來的，網上早前曾傳出一張譚仔單據相，顯示為兩個「特」，是傳說中的雙特辣，該名網民聲稱「本來想叫三特辣，佢（阿姐）初初話有」，不過之後阿姐表示「冇三特辣」。

譚仔阿姐常用字翻譯：
1 勿演 ---> 墨丸
2 畜牲 ---> 竹笙
3 肌肉 ---> 雞肉
4 懶肉 ---> 腩肉
5 豬忍 ---> 豬潤

6 兒蛋 ---> 魚蛋
7 義父 ---> 魚腐
8 仙菜 ---> 生菜
9 凍鏈茶 ---> 凍檸茶
10 凍X死 ---> 凍檸水
Good for quick lunch

result.formatted_address: 2-16 Wang Pok St, Sha Tin, Hong Kong
result.name: Shatin Centre

reviews.text: Although it is not a big shopping mall, there are many local shops, as well as different kind of restaurants. You will find more locals than tourists here, and more shops with Hong Kong characteristics, comparing to New Town Plaza. Staff are very nice and helpful, especially when you need emergency help. You are expected to enjoy a good shopping experience.

Unlike the New Town Plaza, it is safer stay here.
The security guards are professional and willing to help people.
No fancy decorations but it's the best shopping mall nearby.
A good mall for locals, reasonable price, quite crowded

Shatin Centre is in the heart of Shatin and it is a series of many Centers connected with each others on one side there is MTR station and government transport department and under this center there is the main bus terminal and on the other side there is the Shatin Law Courts building 
adjacent to a huge park.
